nodes.text: Tareesh was a man who, in 9 ABY, was involved with New Republic Senator Wyl Lark, and briefly met Lark's former Alphabet Squadron colleagues Chass na Chadic and Yrica Quell. When Lark next met up with Chadic and Quell at their house on Spirana in 11 ABY, Lark informed them he had broken up with Tareesh some months back.
